{"type":"message","id":"01e9f37e","parentId":"478267c7","timestamp":"2026-03-23T04:09:12.985Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering shutdown advice**\n\nI’m thinking about the user’s request regarding Windows shutdown in a group chat. I wonder if I should employ the healthcheck skill, but maybe it’s unnecessary. I could provide concise next steps for the user instead. It might be more helpful to give clear and straightforward instructions on how to go about shutting down Windows in that context, without overcomplicating things. Keeping it simple should be the goal here!","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_066f30902044fa970169c0bce696b881919efc3f21d233382a\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpwLzpSoGIVfokkYmIxpG_6vQj32wzig3ISkJrLpiFOm4VzO1v_A-TSsrbrfToQqx7tA-vfxccSRPiglMYfoKIgRxqCwfrxoO7aQk3qw4g2fLSh_XD2nHSyNzreODAerVDe4LJyMK1Vc1Gv2_q44-y9yTV8LhdZxRU9PdWGmfu6Y_WGGcnpSgnmWwjPpOY26-x3E6x9Kby6NS3HDW3sD5yzLGemOIvEhXh2mmMMEzBmleFXz51cOnmQ1NlUG8C5NeqsBLa3xxl5dD-8F8AJv00vY-mhj61fF1dWy20wxFBitdhX4XU-Vy3Y4lq6nf3-q29AENkv51QkcneTq5XD-RyK3MiQQNY90kVriDwnxUkUczePNx40M3CMKF5wPTRS0-DL80AD38RyQRS1g6e3wVDUkuNyX1aRPc3n1lRsMTA7kxn6bstPXOz2qv9ZfnWeDMQSzHLtombZ1c-wqd9d5G012fQz6N82vsjNjhRVojYN2pTcuj5-MC7B_BBojmpyQk46WvuZr7hG8dSFczSLCHeRplbKN3q6po9daQOKZghBT0sy0f-jh8S8_a6FbDOmb1LHMaFW4uYtOJfvibLbijTiJ1YpMzAIpFuvH1GSFqhPppUA9UC1OHEYW8ufbIlXMOnkOpoiMizVz5LuRHDvE4Ws7pD1g970e72Oqc_8gqlArzComRG6Oi26q_sRwpKbKL-3qis50k406awVIpRA_TddDROO_C-IgupaAl2P0L9YtMiOjYcXzgtZeIuR57mJ7dOpmj1AB_wb9Jg7f1eows6G8RUUy-iYuIB52yICgNPTgb1kj2PYPz-HoFbFn0xMonoIzlHfwQUYJ0pajTmZ7v9IZYiyVRCy2MOKu0DhPHodkUHQvhrK-svb-JkoCFOlgcBkHTsE6rKogOStyTm4hgSzmBpOyoYYMtiglfwUUjFkmhEpjw7qTYTo-edQnHYMRNHfZc5ZK6115DiDffc4kvkrMpX4NVvB7Uoe6WkGogSIr1pZpM=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering shutdown advice**\\n\\nI’m thinking about the user’s request regarding Windows shutdown in a group chat. I wonder if I should employ the healthcheck skill, but maybe it’s unnecessary. I could provide concise next steps for the user instead. It might be more helpful to give clear and straightforward instructions on how to go about shutting down Windows in that context, without overcomplicating things. Keeping it simple should be the goal here!\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] Ok, vậy là ít nhất máy đã lên lại được — đó là dấu hiệu đỡ hơn vụ chết nguồn hẳn.\n\nGiờ anh làm nhanh 4 bước này để xem có tái diễn không:\n\n- **Cắm sạc/kiểm tra nguồn** cho chắc\n- mở **Task Manager** xem CPU/RAM có đang full bất thường không\n- mở **Event Viewer** → `Windows Logs` → `System`  \n  tìm lỗi đúng lúc máy vừa tắt, nhất là:\n  - `Kernel-Power`\n  - `BugCheck`\n  - `unexpected shutdown`\n\n- kiểm tra OpenClaw đã sống lại chưa:\n  - `openclaw status`\n  - `openclaw gateway status`\n\nNếu gateway chưa chạy:\n- `openclaw gateway start`\n\nNếu anh muốn check nhanh nguyên nhân vụ sập máy, gửi em:\n1. máy là **laptop hay desktop**\n2. lúc tắt có **cắm sạc** không\n3. có thấy lỗi `Kernel-Power` không\n\nEm sẽ khoanh vùng cho anh ngay.","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_066f30902044fa970169c0bce9cea08191869237898373a30b\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":710,"output":265,"cacheRead":12032,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13007,"cost":{"input":0.001775,"output":0.003975,"cacheRead":0.003008,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.008758}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774238946140}}
